response.overview: This extra-length history of the RAF covers every significant event from WWI to 2003's invasion of Iraq. Also included is action-packed footage of over one hundred different aircraft types flown by the RAF, from the WWI era Sopwith Camel to the latest Eurofighter Typhoon. Includes four rare short bonus films covering subjects as diverse as Vulcans in the USA and Beaufighters attacking enemy shipping.
response.title: The RAF Story
